---
title: The Difference Between Flexibility and Indecision in Mortgage Design
description: Keeping your options open is not a strategy. Here's how to tell genuine flexibility from financial indecision — and why the difference costs real money.
publishDate: 2026-01-08
category: mortgage-tips
